data.title: Independent School in Tampa Bay
data.meta_description: Berkeley Preparatory School is a private school in Tampa, Florida (pre-kindergarten to twelfth grade). Its a coed, Episcopal day school.
data.text:
#1

Berkeley Preparatory School is a nationally regarded, coed, independent day school in Tampa, Florida, that presents a safe, nurturing environment featuring inspiring teaching, engaged parents, and outstanding resources, including incomparable facilities on a beautiful, 86-acre campus. We offer an exceedingly broad and balanced curriculum, as well as an incredible extracurricular program. Both are enjoyed by an exceptional and diverse community of learners following personalized paths, who relish a supportive culture, the schools Episcopal identity, its ongoing commitment to continual self-improvement, and a deeply authentic dedication to making a positive difference in the world. From preschool to twelfth grade, our educational philosophy is to develop and expect strong character, promote innovation and growth, and desire excellence in all that we do. Berkeley motivates students to become well-rounded individuals, as well as caring and successful adults. Our graduates attend some of the finest colleges and universities in the countryand become part of a powerful and close-knit alumni network. Simply put, the educational journey at Berkeley is truly extraordinary.
